Changelog:

Mi 8:
- Kernel: 4.9.158
- Improved power efficiency in idle
- Improved OP like gesures handling
- Simple 2.35
- Upstream sched changes
- Simple low memory killer
- Optimised memcmp
- Properly support f2fs
- Sound control added
- Dynmice stune boosting refactored and cleaned up
- Boosting is less agressive for greater battery
- Schedutil changes for lower latency
- Improve power usage in idle
- Work queue powersaving enabled by default
- Improved kernel timers
- SElinux does not require auditing 
- Better scrolling
- Added Dirac sound enhancer PROPERLY 
- Other various optimisations 

Rom:
- Version 2.3
- Lockscreen visualizer
- Fixed media art cover
- Fixed some statusbar clock issues
- OP like gestures tweaks
- Ability to turn off conditions/suggestions in settings
- CAF touch responce optimization
- Launcher: switch to latest LawnChair v2
- Update translations
- Filemanager (DocumentsUI) fixes
- Screenrecord 18:9 res support
- Other fixes and improvements
